## 🚀 使用方式

### 安裝與啟動
```bash
pip install fastmcp
fastmcp run goldenegg_plugin.py

# 或使用啟動腳本
bash start.sh
```

### Tools 使用範例

#### 儲存 OCR 解析結果
```json
{
  "tool": "save_holdings",
  "args": {
    "source": "ocr",
    "data": [
      {
        "symbol": "2330.TW",
        "name": "台積電",
        "shares": 1000,
        "avg_cost": 580.0,
        "currency": "TWD",
        "retrieved_at": "2025-07-16T12:00:00+08:00"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

#### 查詢券商持股
```json
{
  "tool": "get_holdings",
  "args": {
    "source": "broker",
    "broker": "fubon"
  }
}
```

### Resources 使用範例

#### 查詢券商配置
```
GET goldenegg://broker_configs
```

#### 查詢 OCR 歷史
```
GET goldenegg://ocr_history/ocr_20250716_01
```

